Have you ever seen something
coming, and done nothing to stop it?

507
01:07:14,540 --> 01:07:19,440
- We all have.
- Something bad. It happened . . .

508
01:07:20,579 --> 01:07:23,079
. . . and you didn't do anything.

509
01:07:27,498 --> 01:07:32,264
