I think we just need to get wasted.

512
01:08:17,936 --> 01:08:19,769
Come on.

513
01:08:25,935 --> 01:08:28,635
I want to live at the beach
some day.

514
01:08:29,335 --> 01:08:34,435
Shit! I left the keys.
I'll get them.

515
01:08:54,014 --> 01:08:57,880
- Kelly?
- Suzie . . .

516
01:08:59,534 --> 01:09:02,534
It's me.

517
01:09:05,693 --> 01:09:11,993
I was worried about you. I thought
we'd get together one last time.

518
01:09:13,412 --> 01:09:15,946
- Are you mad at me?
- No, no.

519
01:09:16,612 --> 01:09:20,612
I should have said more
about the part you should play.

520
01:09:21,572 --> 01:09:24,106
We'll go through it all
again tonight.

521
