- Just the idea that he would . . .

546
01:13:22,319 --> 01:13:25,119
I heard he was pretty tight
with the kids.

547
01:13:25,837 --> 01:13:29,670
- You and he were pals, right?
- He got me on the sailing team.

548
01:13:30,598 --> 01:13:33,064
