partner.

566
01:16:08,789 --> 01:16:15,989
- And if the teeth aren't Suzie's?
- If I'm wrong, I'll give this up.

567
01:16:58,826 --> 01:17:02,659
- Hello.
- I want to see you.

568
01:17:03,585 --> 01:17:07,218
