- Since when?

577
01:18:05,742 --> 01:18:09,475
She didn't come home last night.
We found her car.

578
01:18:10,381 --> 01:18:15,015
- Ray thinks she was murdered.
- I don't know what to tell you.

579
01:18:16,102 --> 01:18:21,569
- Tell me where you were last night.
- I don't have to, do I?

580
01:18:26,220 --> 01:18:30,087
Come here.
I want to show you something.

581
01:18:41,020 --> 01:18:43,153
