623
01:23:45,323 --> 01:23:47,489
Mr. Duquette . . .

624
01:23:49,361 --> 01:23:52,595
This investigation is concluded.
You're dismissed.

625
01:24:18,240 --> 01:24:20,773
Thank you.

626
01:25:12,477 --> 01:25:14,944
Howdy, partner.

627
01:25:15,597 --> 01:25:19,264
I wasn't expecting you
until tomorrow.

628
01:25:23,197 --> 01:25:26,331
- Nice girlfriend !
- Why wasn't Kelly just framed?

629
01:25:27,117 --> 01:25:31,550
- The bitch shot me.
- Can't cops disarm people?

630
01:25:32,596 --> 01:25:34,896
Shoot them in the leg?

631
01:25:35,517 --> 01:25:40,617
Did you get squeamish after
you killed Suzie with a wine bottle?

632
01:25:41,795 --> 01:25:44,529
Kelly wasn't supposed to die.

633
