I could use a deckhand.

642
01:26:32,792 --> 01:26:35,592
Here's to large bank accounts.

643
01:26:37,552 --> 01:26:41,252
Lighten up, partner.
You're a rich man.

644
01:26:44,071 --> 01:26:47,205
