I don't understand a word
you just said.

655
01:28:10,627 --> 01:28:15,160
Follow this line, and see
if you can see what it's snagged on.

656
01:28:17,827 --> 01:28:20,727
You're killing me.

657
01:28:27,826 --> 01:28:31,726
- You mean this thing?
- That's it. See anything?

658
01:28:36,705 --> 01:28:39,305
Look a little lower.
That's it.

659
01:28:48,624 --> 01:28:51,858
Guess I forgot to tell you, Ray.

660
01:28:52,665 --> 01:28:57,032
"One hand for the boat,
the other for yourself."

661
01:29:21,904 --> 01:29:25,770
