- I thought you looked different.

671
01:30:42,179 --> 01:30:46,579
- I was hoping you would talk to me.
- About Suzie?

672
01:30:47,619 --> 01:30:52,252
Actually I was wondering if you
would talk to me about Ray Duquette.

673
01:30:56,578 --> 01:31:01,978
He used to come here. He had
a thing going with one of the girls.

674
01:31:03,217 --> 01:31:05,917
"Girls" . . . over at the Glades.

675
01:31:07,377 --> 01:31:10,877
