from what I hear.

676
01:31:11,737 --> 01:31:15,104
- Does she still work there?
- Not after that night.

677
01:31:15,936 --> 01:31:20,803
All I know is, next morning
she was gone and a boy was dead.

678
01:31:21,936 --> 01:31:26,069
A Seminole kid named Davy.
He had a crush on Ray's whore.

679
01:31:30,255 --> 01:31:34,455
